samclient~ - SAM client external for Pd
	Developed by Zachary Seldess, Sonic Arts R&D, Qualcomm Institute, Calit2, UC San Diego


Dependencies: 
	streaming-audio (http://code.google.com/p/streaming-audio/)
	Qt (http://qt-project.org)
	Pd (http://puredata.info)

Installation:
	1. Run './configure'

	2. Update the following variables in samclient/makefile:
		QTSDK_DIR (QT SDK install directory)
		SA_DIR (Streaming-audio install directory)
	
	3. Place makefile.subdir and samclient/ in <Pd application/Contents/Resources/

	4. Run make inside samclient directory to build Pd external
